						               													<description>Vrahode is an adventure/dungeon crawl board game series. The game is a solo/co-op game for 1-6 players, 14+ and includes Weathervane Games proprietary 3D terrain system called Harbinger which is used for dynamic multi level spaces. In this 2nd expansion we find at the root of the chaos reigns an entity of immense power. Its reach and influence is ever growing and twisting the minds of everything it touches. Into that maelstrom of corruption is precisely where our path leads us. There will be no rest until this enemy is eliminated because soon its tendrils of control may consume us all! This expansion features new enemies, tons of new quests in in the Overlands, Underlands and at sea! Lots of new Harbinger tiles including the Dungeon Riser which allows you to raise an 18X18&amp;quot; tile up to two levels and making five level dungeons possible! All games in the series are part of the Vrahode Game System which invites players to generate their own content adding to the expanding lore of Vrahode!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
